Very nice move here by me - almost languid, lazy... seemingly innocuos but indefinitely sealing a victory for me. If I remember correctly, it was this move that earned the late Baron Borabottle his easy victory of then-no.1 Van Banguilugud, in the Russo-Frencho-Indo-American championship final.
